{"tid":483460,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【長氣怪預備】WhatsApp推新功能 錄音鍵上鎖任你講","createTime":"2017-11-29T06:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T10:13:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"14a502baf1f302105cd9c4c111bcc44afbeb3965","tid":483460,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171129/large/1511938206_dd23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171129%2Flarge%2F1511938206_dd23.jpg&h=00a2eaa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp再推新功能，今次啱晒一班喜歡錄一大段語音訊息的用家。在不方便打字時，或難以用文字解釋的情況下，語音訊息的確非常方便。今次更新增加錄音上鎖功能，按下錄音鍵上推後就可放開手，錄製長語音訊息時就不用按到手抽筋，或未錄完就發送出去。不過都到了要錄長語音訊息的地步，為什麼不直接打電話呢？<br />\n<br />\n另外Whatsapp也加入畫中畫播放YouTube片的功能，可直接在WhatsApp中觀看YouTube片，跳轉至其他對話時也可繼續播放。不過似乎尚未正式啟用，想試就要再等等。<br />\n<br />\n文：梁志穎<br />\n攝影：周旭文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20171129/57519297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171129%2F57519297&d=jQ8xyZDsqHejrt5cQn20JL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5984d5c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171129%2F57519297&h=8f8ec618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20171129/57519297</a>"},{"pid":"1b62fae5bcde8f5d2f1a9278e93eb682640d5f0f","tid":483460,"uid":4285,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:59:08.000Z","msg":"telegram 晨早有啦"},{"pid":"ad1119f6a7a0a0d86123638ee9924aa7eaed041b","tid":483460,"uid":33206,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:01:23.000Z","msg":"屌我仲以為係lock左個錄音功能等對方唔可以用費事煩到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93134cccfdb57a9d132f17d5261