ca5732b43370e7c6b2f44e0d","tid":483460,"uid":30552,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"成日都錄錄下洗咗，真係錄到火都嚟，個新功能真係太好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係用嚟同我阿婆講嘢，聽聲好啲嘅。我同佢有時差，又唔係話有好多嘢講，得閒留個言，佢瞓醒或者得閒覆返我。同埋佢唔識用whatsapp聽電話，所以錄音係最好。"},{"pid":"fe64a6837e0ecdd09af5c7328a735b2ea6d74f85","tid":483460,"uid":24570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:56:07.000Z","msg":"錄咁耐點聽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9409b68f9c8adc46380915430a1698199d724ac9","tid":483460,"uid":39527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"最撚憎人錄音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc453f1bd46dcd53c5877caa8b97e91c60e821b4","tid":483460,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T08:56:57.000Z","msg":"食屎啦屌你老母 錄音撚死全家"},{"pid":"aa44a70aac50e8ced71b1759123535546c9813ca","tid":483460,"uid":12853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"不樓都唔聽 <br />\n啲錄音都唔方重要架啦 仲要整長佢"},{"pid":"e0861fb0a709e3f0cc3e30bec152f1a3bee7d89f","tid":483460,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我仲以為係lock左個錄音功能等對方唔可以用費事煩到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 呢個正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f446154a4836801f7106ce30b5416b25088975a","tid":483460,"uid":411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"左抄右抄telegram，係未抄到自動播下一段錄音，we7 telegram有咗九年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{